715309f-a.title: Manhattan: 124th Street (East) - Park Avenue
715309f-a.text:
1O1-127 East 124th Street, at, adjoining, and east of the N.E.
corner of Park Avenue. The one-story buildings in the foreground
are the J. M. Horton Ice Cream Company. In the centre is the
rear of Proctor's 125th Street Theatre.
July 244, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
